quotas.name: Gujarat Government Seats
quotas.tooltip_content:
**Eligibility for the Quota : Gujarat Government Seats**

X and XII passed from Gujarat (CBSE/ICSE/Gujarat Board/Int. Board/NIOS) in B Group (PCB) or AB group (PCMB). Should also be born in Gujarat State or be a Domicile of Gujarat State. Also sons/ daughters of 
1. AIS officers(IAS/IPS/IFS) allotted to Gujarata State serving outside Gujarat (or)
2. Gujarat Govt employees posted outside Gujarat are also eligible
Also candidates who have studied in Jawahar Navodya Vidyalaya of Gujarat till Std VIII and studied under Navodaya scheme till 12th will also be eligible 
3. Defence personnel who are domicile of Gujarat but posted outside Gujarat
Ineligible: Those who passed through supplementary examinations in that year wont be eligible

Also candidates who have studied in Jawahar Navodya Vidyalaya of Gujarat till Std VIII and studied under Navodaya scheme till 12th will also be eligible 
3. Defence personnel who are domicile of Gujarat but posted outside Gujarat
Ineligible: Those who passed through supplementary examinations in that year wont be eligible

X and XII passed from Gujarat (CBSE/ICSE/Gujarat Board/Int. Board/NIOS) in B Group (PCB) or AB group (PCMB). Should also be born in Gujarat State or be a Domicile of Gujarat State. Also sons/ daughters of 
1. AIS officers(IAS/IPS/IFS) allotted to Gujarata State serving outside Gujarat (or)
2. Gujarat Govt employees posted outside Gujarat are also eligible
Also candidates who have studied in Jawahar Navodya Vidyalaya of Gujarat till Std VIII and studied under Navodaya scheme till 12th will also be eligible 
3. Defence personnel who are domicile of Gujarat but posted outside Gujarat
Ineligible: Those who passed through supplementary examinations in that year wont be eligible

X and XII passed from Gujarat (CBSE/ICSE/Gujarat Board/Int. Board/NIOS) in B Group (PCB) or AB group (PCMB). Should also be born in Gujarat State or be a Domicile of Gujarat State. Also sons/ daughters of 
1. AIS officers(IAS/IPS/IFS) allotted to Gujarata State serving outside Gujarat (or)
2. Gujarat Govt employees posted outside Gujarat are also eligible
Also candidates who have studied in Jawahar Navodya Vidyalaya of Gujarat till Std VIII and studied under Navodaya scheme till 12th will also be eligible 
3. Defence personnel who are domicile of Gujarat but posted outside Gujarat
Ineligible: Those who passed through supplementary examinations in that year wont be eligible

**Eligibility for the Quota : Gujarat Government Seats**

X and XII passed from Gujarat (CBSE/ICSE/Gujarat Board/Int. Board/NIOS) in B Group (PCB) or AB group (PCMB). Should also be born in Gujarat State or be a Domicile of Gujarat State. Also sons/ daughters of 
1. AIS officers(IAS/IPS/IFS) allotted to Gujarata State serving outside Gujarat (or)
2. Gujarat Govt employees posted outside Gujarat are also eligible
Also candidates who have studied in Jawahar Navodya Vidyalaya of Gujarat till Std VIII and studied under Navodaya scheme till 12th will also be eligible 
3. Defence personnel who are domicile of Gujarat but posted outside Gujarat
Ineligible: Those who passed through supplementary examinations in that year wont be eligible
